Festiviz Privacy Policy
Last updated: October 2025

Festiviz (“the App”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your data.

1. We only collect the minimum data required to authenticate your TikTok account via TikTok’s secure OAuth 2.0 API.
2. We do not store, sell, or share any personal data, videos, or analytics outside your authorized use.
3. Access tokens are securely stored and used only for posting on your behalf.
4. We use Google Cloud (or equivalent) to manage and process automation tasks securely.
5. You may revoke access at any time via TikTok’s app settings.
6. For inquiries, contact us at support@metamedia.com.

This Privacy Policy complies with TikTok’s Developer Terms and global privacy standards.
